                    <div class="newsMsg" itemprop="articleBody">
                        Sony於今（12）日舉辦「The future of gaming」PS5遊戲發表會，並正式公開PlayStation5主機外觀，與各種類型周邊。<br><br><div id="replaceMedia" class="video-container"><iframe width="560" height="315" allowfullscreen src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RkC0l4iekYo?unshow=false"></iframe></div id="replaceMedia">&nbsp;<br><br>作為本次「The future of gaming」最後壓軸大戲，PS5本體果然沒讓玩家失望。與先前發布的手把DualSense相同，PS5本體以白色為主色調，並搭配黑色與藍色光條，營造出科技感十足的外觀。<br><br><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/10-1.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/11-1.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/102614801_4073318229377552_4274867393653410283_o.jpg" alt=""></figure>不僅如此，Sony看準未來數位版的市場，更大膽推出沒有光碟機、純數位版的PS5。外觀基本上無太大差異，<br><br><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3-1.jpg" alt=""></figure>另外，Sony也公開各項周邊設備，包括3D音效耳機、媒體遙控器、全新HD攝影機等等。<br><br><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/4-1.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/5-1.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/8-1.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/9-1.jpg" alt=""></figure><figure class="image"><img src="https://game.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/6.jpg" alt=""></figure>PlayStation5預計於今年聖誕假期推出，目前價格仍未公開。<br><br>
                        <p></p>
